Let the heart beat like the first time</p>
<p>Kiss me, pray<br />
May all the world&#8217;s candles burn for us</p>
<p>Stay tonight, when everyone threatens me<br />
Stay, embrace me like a child<br />
Stay, when all my love is you<br />
Stay, to hold me when the angels fall asleep</p>
